A wani taron manema labarai, kyaftin mai tsaron rai Larry Giles ya ce an ga wani kifi a yankin 'yan makonni da suka wuce, amma an ce ba shi da wata illa.
Giles ya kara da cewa wanda aka kashe ya samu mummunan rauni a jikinsa.
Hukumomin kasar sun rufe bakin tekun Casablad daga bakin rairayin bakin teku na Ponto zuwa bakin rairayin bakin teku na Ecinitas zuwa Swami na tsawon awanni 48 saboda dalilai na bincike da kuma tsaro.
Giles ya ce akwai nau'in kifi fiye da 135 a yankin, amma yawancin su ana ɗaukansu marasa lahani.
