Peter Jones ya fusata bayan da Holly Willoughby ta janye daga yarjejeniyar fam miliyan 11
Tauraron 'Dragons Den' Peter Jones ya yi murabus bayan da mai gabatar da shirye-shirye Holly Willoughby ta janye daga yarjejeniyar £11m da ta yi da kamfanin lifestyle na ta domin ta mayar da hankali kan sabon kwangilarta da kamfanin Marks and Spencer da ITV
Willoughby ba shi da lokacin da zai yi wa Truly, wadda ita ce mai sayar da kayan gida da kayan ado.
Kamfanin Kwekwe ya yi daidai da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop.
Mai gabatar da shirin "This Morning" mai shekara 37 ya sanar da ficewarsa daga shirin a shafinsa na Instagram.
Holly Willoughby ta fusata da Peter Jones, tauraruwar Dragons Den, ta hanyar janyewa daga kasuwancin su na rayuwa mai kayatarwa a karshe na minti, kuma yanzu tana shirin mayar da hankali kan sabbin kwantiraginta na kwangila da Marks & Spencer da ITV.
Majiyoyin sun ce Jones ya yi "hatsari" a ranar Talata a wani taro mai cike da tashin hankali da aka yi a hedkwatar kamfanin Jones da ke Marlow, a Buckinhamshire, inda tauraruwar ta amince cewa sabon kwangilarsa na fam miliyan 1.5 ba zai ba da isasshen lokaci ga Truly, mai sayar da kayan abinci da kayan sawa ba.
An kwatanta kamfanin da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop, kuma an yi ta yin fare-faren cewa zai ninka dukiyar Willoughby da aka kiyasta fam miliyan 11.
Bayan Willoughby, mai shekara 37, ya sanar a shafinsa na Instagram cewa zai bar Truly, Jones ya tashi daga Birtaniya zuwa daya daga cikin gidajen hutun da ya yi.
A cewar wata majiya, "'Truly" ita ce babbar manufar da Holly ta fara.
Wannan shi ne shirin da ya tsara na dogon lokaci, don ya samu abin biyan bukata na shekaru 20 masu zuwa.
Amma, duk da haka, matakin da ya ɗauka ya ba mu mamaki.
Babu wanda ya yi imani da abin da ya faru a ranar Talata da ke kusa da ranar da za a buga.
A hedkwatar Marlow, akwai kayayyaki da yawa da ake so a sayar.
Mai gabatar da shirin na This Morning yana daya daga cikin fitattun jaruman Birtaniya, kuma 'yan bincike sun ce ficewarsa zai iya jawo wa kamfanin asarar miliyoyin daloli saboda saka hannun jari a kayayyaki daga gindi zuwa kyandir da tufafi da kayayyakin gida, ba ma maganar jinkiri a buga shi.
Kuma hakan zai iya sa a daina abokantakarmu.
A cikin shekaru goma, Willoughby, uwar 'ya'ya uku, da mijinta Dan Baldwin, sun yi abota da Jones da matarsa Tara Capp.
Willoughby ya shirya Cappin Truly a 2016 kuma Jones, 52, ya zama shugaban a watan Maris.
Ma'auratan suna hutu tare, kuma Jones yana da kashi 40 cikin ɗari na kamfanin Baldwin na TV.
Willoughby zai zama sabon jakadan M&S kuma zai maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin mai gabatar da shirin I'm A Celebrity na ITV.
