"Ina kokarin sanya kaina a wasa don samun kwallon kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaq suna wasa a gaba sosai, don haka ina kokarin samar wa kaina da lokaci sosai", in ji Sturridge a shafin LiverpoolFC.com.
"Na ga Kanten yana zuwa, sai na ɗauki harbi ɗaya kuma na harba harbin ba tare da tunani ba".
Chelsea ta ci wasan 1-0 a ragar da ta tashi daga Belgium Eden Hazard ya ci kwallo a minti na 25.
A wannan yanayin, dan wasan Blues ya ba da kyautar Mateo Kovacic, kafin ya gudu a kusa da tsakiyar filin kuma ya yi tsalle a cikin filin Liverpool.
Kovacic ya buga kwallo a cikin filin tsakiya.
Bayan haka, sai ya saki Hazard a cikin filin wasan tare da kwallaye mai ban mamaki.
Hazard ya tsere daga tsaron Liverpool, ya wuce Alison Becker da ƙafarsa ta hagu a kusurwar baya.
Liverpool za ta fafata a wasan zakarun Turai a filin wasa na San Paolo da ke birnin Naples na kasar Italiya a karfe 3 na yammacin ranar Laraba.
Chelsea za ta fafata da UEFA a gasar cin kofin Turai da za a buga da Videoton a ranar Alhamis da karfe 3 a Landan.
