A ranar Talata, mutane fiye da miliyan 20 sun kalli wani shiri da aka watsa a gidajen talabijin na ƙasashe shida, inda Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ke neman a naɗa shi a matsayin alƙali a Kotun Koli, da Christine Blasey Ford, wadda ke tuhumar shi da laifin lalata a shekarun 1980 suka ba da shaida mai ban sha'awa.
