Kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa adadin mutanen da ke dauke da kwayar cutar HIV da kuma wadanda ke fama da cutar AIDS a kasar ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Hukumomin kiwon lafiya sun ce cutar ta shafi mutane fiye da 820,000 a kasar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai, an samu kimanin sabbin mutane 40,000 da suka kamu da cutar.
Mafi yawan sabbin masu kamuwa da cutar sun kamu ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya kawo sauyi a kididdigar da muka yi a baya.
A dā, cutar HIV ta yadu da sauri a wasu ɓangarorin ƙasar Sin ta hanyar karɓan jini da aka yi wa ƙwari.
Amma, bisa ga hukuma da ke kula da lafiyar jama'a a ƙasar Sin, waɗanda suka halarci wani taro a lardin Yunnan, an rage yawan masu kamuwa da cutar HIV da ake yi ta wannan hanyar zuwa kusan babu.
Amma bayan shekara guda, adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV a China ya ƙaru da 100,000.
Cutar kwayar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i wata babbar matsala ce a tsakanin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma ana nuna wariya ga LGBT.
Bincike ya nuna cewa saboda ra'ayin mazan jiya game da al'adun kasar, kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na maza da ke yin jima'i da maza za su yi aure da mata.
