Wanda ya kirkiri yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin kafa sabuwar hanyar sadarwa ta yanar gizo don ya yi adawa da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kafa wani kamfani da ke da niyyar yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikinsa, Inrupt, wani kamfani ne da aka gina a kan tsarin Berners-Lee na Solid Open Source.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar yanke shawara inda za a adana bayanan su, da kuma wanda zai iya samun damar kowane bayanai.
A wata hira da ya yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa Inrupt dariya cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulki duniya".
"Dole ne a yi hakan yanzu", ya ce, yana magana ne game da kamfani da ya kafa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasaha na Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar 'tashar bayanan sirri' ko POD.
Yana iya ƙunsar jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin abubuwan tunawa, kalandar, laburaren kiɗa, da sauran kayan aikin mutum da na sana'a.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk a cikin wannan burauzar a lokaci guda.
Abu na musamman game da bayanan sirri shi ne cewa yana da ikon mai amfani ya zaɓi irin bayanan da zai iya samu.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "karfi na mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar shugaban kamfanin, John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da albarkatu, da hanyoyin da ake bukata da kuma kwarewar da ake bukata don kawo Solid a cikin kowa.
Kamfanin na yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani jirgin ruwa na tsaro wanda IBM ya saya, wasu masu haɓaka masu aiki tare da aikin, da kuma al'umma na masu ba da izinin ba da izini.
Masu haɓaka fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen rarraba tare da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt, wanda aka fara amfani da shi a wannan makon.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba za su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba game da samar wa mutane da cikakken canji, wanda zai juya duk tsarin kasuwancin su a cikin dare daya.
Ba ma tambayar su ko sun yarda da abin.
A cikin wani rubutu da aka buga a cikin Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "aikin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu don daidaito da ingancin sabon hanyar sadarwar da aka gina don Solid".
