An ce lamarin ya faru ne a watan Yunin 2009 a wani dakin hotel na Palms Hotel and Casino a Las Vegas.
An ce Ronaldo da Mayorgan sun saba zuwa wani gidan rawa, kuma sun koma gidan mai wasan, inda aka ce ya yi mata fyaɗe ta hanyar daɗaɗa, kamar yadda aka bayyana a cikin takardun da aka gabatar a Kotun Yankin Clark County na Nevada.
Mayorga ta ce Ronaldo ya durƙusa bayan da aka ce ya yi abin da ya faru, ya ce "Ni mutum ne mai kirki kashi 99 cikin 100", amma kashi ɗaya cikin 100 ya ba da kunya.
A cewar Ronaldo, a cikin takardun da aka samu, an tabbatar da cewa ma'auratan sun yi jima'i, amma sun yarda da juna.
Mayorga ta kuma ce ta je ofishin 'yan sanda ta dauki hoton raunin da aka yi mata a asibiti, amma daga baya ta yanke shawarar sulhu saboda "tsoro na ramuwar gayya" da kuma "damuwar cewa za a wulakanta ta a bainar jama'a".
