Yanayin ruwan Red Tide: Yanayin da ke sauka a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
A cikin wani rahoto da Hukumar Kifi da Dabbobi ta Florida ta fitar kwanan nan, an ga raguwar zalɓe a yankin da ke kusa da Tampa Bay.
FWC ta ce an samu rahotanni da ke nuna cewa akwai wuraren da ake samun yashi a wurare dabam-dabam a cikin yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlottesville da Collier County, wanda hakan ya nuna cewa akwai yiwuwar raguwar yawan yashi.
Red tide turtles suna da yawa a gabar teku, kimanin mil 130 daga Pinellas zuwa kudancin Lee County.
Ana iya samun raƙuman ruwa mai zurfi mil 10 daga gabar tekun Hillsborough County, amma ba a yawan samun su kamar yadda aka samu a makon da ya gabata.
An kuma gano wata sanwar da ke dauke da kwayar cutar Red Tide a yankin Pasco.
An samu rahotannin matsakaicin yawa a gabar tekun Pinellas County a makon da ya gabata, wanda ya kasance daga ƙananan zuwa manyan a gabar tekun Hillsborough County, daga ƙananan zuwa manyan a gabar tekun Manatee County da Sarasota County, daga ƙananan zuwa matsakaicin a gabar tekun Charlotte County, daga ƙananan zuwa manyan a gabar tekun Lee County da Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da bayar da rahoton alamun numfashi a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
A cikin mako guda da ya gabata, babu wani rahoton rashin numfashi da aka samu a arewa maso yammacin Florida.
